SEARCH
======

GET /search
-----------
params:
	- q = string (search query)
	- offset = int (default 0)
	- limit = int (default 10)
	- includeAlbums = 1/0 (default 0)
	- includeUsers = 1/0 (default 0)

todos:
	- introduce fields
	- introduce filters (see the endpoints GET /albums and GET /users for inspiration)
	- better pagination